  "english": [
    "mean <b>that even in the earlier</b> cases, where he did not become irritated, they disagree with regard to vows of exhortation and hold that these vows are indeed valid, <b>and</b> can one <b>conclude from</b> here that <b>the Rabbis disagree with him?</b> The Gemara concludes: <b>Conclude from</b> here that this is so.",
    "With regard to the practical conclusion of this dispute, the Gemara asks: <b>What</b> halakhic conclusion <b>was</b> reached <b>about</b> this matter? Does the <i>halakha</i> follow the opinion of the Rabbis or that of Rabbi Eliezer ben Ya’akov? The Gemara answers: <b>Come</b> and <b>hear</b> that <b>which Rav Huna said:</b> The <b><i>halakha</i> is in accordance with</b> the opinion of <b>Rabbi Eliezer ben Ya’akov. And so said Rav Adda bar Ahava:</b> The <b><i>halakha</i> is in accordance with</b> the opinion of <b>Rabbi Eliezer ben Ya’akov.</b>",
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> <b>Vows of exaggeration</b> that the Sages dissolved without a request to a halakhic authority, as described in the first mishna in the chapter, include the following examples. If <b>one said</b> concerning a certain item: It is <b><i>konam</i></b> for me <b>if I did not see on this road</b> as many people <b>as those who ascended</b> from <b>Egypt,</b> or if he said: It is <i>konam</i> for me <b>if I did not see a snake</b> as large <b>as</b> the <b>beam of an olive press,</b> in these cases the speaker did not intend to vow but used hyperbole to demonstrate a point, and it is understood by others that the expression is not to be taken literally.",
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> <b>A Sage taught:</b> Items rendered forbidden through <b>vows of exaggeration [<i>havai</i>] are permitted;</b> items rendered forbidden through <b>oaths of exaggeration are forbidden.</b> Since oaths are very severe, one does not take an oath unless he intends it seriously. Therefore, it is not viewed as an oath of exaggeration.",
    "The Gemara clarifies the details: <b>What are the circumstances</b> of the case of <b>oaths of exaggeration? If we say that</b> it is when one <b>said:</b> I take <b>an oath if I did not see on this road</b> as many people as those who ascended from Egypt, <b>is he saying anything?</b> This statement is not formulated in the form of an oath and therefore has no validity at all, even if he was serious.",
    "The Gemara answers: <b>Abaye said that</b> in a case <b>where one says:</b> I take <b>an oath that I saw</b> on this road as many people as those who ascended from Egypt, the oath is valid. If he did not see that many people, he has taken a false oath. <b>Rava said to him: If so, why do I</b> need <b>to say</b> this; it is not a novelty? <b>And furthermore,</b> it <b>teaches</b> that the case of an oath is <b>similar to</b> that of <b>a vow:</b> Just as in the case of a vow he speaks of not seeing, so too with regard to an oath he must be speaking of not seeing. <b>Rather, Rava said:</b> An oath of exaggeration is <b>where he says:</b> All the <b>produce of the world shall be forbidden to me by an oath if I did not see on this road</b> as many people <b>as those</b> who <b>ascended</b> from <b>Egypt.</b>",
    "<b>Ravina said to Rav Ashi: And perhaps this man saw an anthill and called them:</b> Those <b>who ascended</b> from <b>Egypt,</b> because the quantity of ants was so numerous, <b>and he took an oath properly.</b> Why, then, do we say that this is an oath taken in vain?"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>דַּאֲפִילּוּ בְּקַמַּיְיתָא, וּשְׁמַע מִינַּהּ פְּלִיגִי רַבָּנַן"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עֲלֵיהּ. שְׁמַע מִינַּהּ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>מַאי הָוֵי עֲלַהּ? תָּא שְׁמַע, דְּאָמַר"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "רַב הוּנָא: הֲלָכָה כְּרַבִּי אֱלִיעֶזֶר בֶּן יַעֲקֹב, וְכֵן"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אָמַר רַב אַדָּא בַּר אַהֲבָה: הֲלָכָה כְּרַבִּי"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֱלִיעֶזֶר בֶּן יַעֲקֹב. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> נִדְרֵי הֲבַאי, אָמַר:"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״קֻוֽנָּם אִם לֹא רָאִיתִי בַּדֶּרֶךְ הַזֶּה כְּעוֹלֵי"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִצְרַיִם״, ״אִם לֹא רָאִיתִי נָחָשׁ כְּקוֹרַת בֵּית הַבַּד״."
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> תָּנָא: נִדְרֵי הֲבַאי — מוּתָּרִין, שָׁבוּעוֹת הֲבַאי —"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲסוּרִין. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>הֵיכִי דָּמֵי שָׁבוּעוֹת הֲבַאי?"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אִילֵימָא דְּאָמַר ״שְׁבוּעָה אִם לֹא רָאִיתִי בַּדֶּרֶךְ הַזֶּה״ —"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִידַּעַם קָאָמַר?! <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר אַבָּיֵי: דְּאָמַר ״שְׁבוּעָה"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁרָאִיתִי״. אֲמַר לֵיהּ רָבָא: אִם כֵּן לְמָה לִי"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְמֵימַר? וְעוֹד: דּוּמְיָא דְּנֶדֶר קָתָנֵי! אֶלָּא אָמַר"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "רָבָא, בְּאוֹמֵר: ״יֵאָסְרוּ פֵּירוֹת הָעוֹלָם עָלַי"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בִּשְׁבוּעָה אִם לֹא רָאִיתִי בַּדֶּרֶךְ הַזֶּה כְּעוֹלֵי"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִצְרַיִם״. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֲמַר לֵיהּ רָבִינָא לְרַב אָשֵׁי: וְדִלְמָא הַאי"
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "גַּבְרָא קִינָּא דְשׁוּמְשְׁמָנֵי חֲזָא וְאַסֵּיק לְהוֹן שְׁמָא ״עוֹלֵי מִצְרַיִם״, וְשַׁפִּיר מִשְׁתְּבַע?"
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>אפי'</b> <b>בקמייתא.</b> הנך דלעיל ש\"מ:"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>מאי</b> <b>הוי</b> <b>עלה.</b> אי הוי הלכתא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כוותיה דר' אליעזר דהוי נדרי זרוזין"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ומותר: <b>אמר</b> <b>ליה</b> <b>רבא.</b> א\"כ"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מתניתא דאמר שבועה שראיתי בדרך"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הזה: <b>למה</b> <b>לי</b> <b>למימר.</b> דאסור"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דהיינו שבועה גמורה ודאי כאילו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אמר שבועה שאכלתי: <b>ועודי</b> <b>דומיא</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>דנדר</b> <b>קתני.</b> שבועות (נדרי)"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הבאי אסורין דמשמע דקאמר בלשון"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "נדר ושבועה: <b>אלא</b> <b>אמר</b> <b>רבא.</b> קאמר הכי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "יאסרו כל פירות העולם עלי בשבועה:"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>אם</b> <b>לא</b> <b>ראיתי.</b> ולא קאמר שראיתי: <b>אמר</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>ליה</b> <b>רבינא.</b> אמאי אסורות ודלמא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שפיר אישתבע לדעתיה דידיה: <b>דלמא</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>קינא</b> <b>דשומשמני.</b> נמלות מקובצות הרבה"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ראה ביחד כעולי מצרים דאפשר:"
    }
  ],
